                            <comment id="14565636" author="khmarbaise" created="Fri, 29 May 2015 23:21:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1682566&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;r1682566&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14957189" author="raelik" created="Wed, 14 Oct 2015 16:21:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Actually, it appears that the logic in the fix commited in r1682566 is reversed:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeHeader panelHeader&quot; style=&quot;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-style: solid;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;MinijarFilter.java - Line 223-234&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; ( classesTotal == 0 )
        {
            log.info( &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Minimized &quot;&lt;/span&gt; + classesTotal + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot; -&amp;gt; &quot;&lt;/span&gt; + classesKept + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot; (&quot;&lt;/span&gt; + 100 * classesKept / classesTotal
                + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;%)&quot;&lt;/span&gt; );
        }
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt;
        {
            log.info( &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Minimized &quot;&lt;/span&gt; + classesTotal + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot; -&amp;gt; &quot;&lt;/span&gt; + classesKept );
        }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;That should be &lt;tt&gt;if ( classesTotal != 0 )&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14957206" author="mclean" created="Wed, 14 Oct 2015 16:30:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Agreed.  The logic appears to be reversed and should cause the same issue again.  Re-opening the issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14957399" author="khmarbaise" created="Wed, 14 Oct 2015 18:01:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fix committed see &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MSHADE-209&quot; title=&quot;[REGRESSION] &amp;quot;java.lang.ArithmeticException: / by zero&amp;quot; in MinijarFilter&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MSHADE-209&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MSHADE-209&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. So i will close here. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
